		<h1 class="entry-title">Testimonials</h1>
	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><span style="font-family: Book Antiqua,Palatino; font-size: medium;">We like to direct people to our<a href="https://plus.google.com/108553095314370000537/about?gl=us&amp;hl=en"> Google Places page</a> when it comes to testimonials because of two reasons:</span></p>
<ol>
<li><span style="font-family: Book Antiqua,Palatino; font-size: medium;">It shows an outstanding track record proving that we are an established business.</span></li>
<li><span style="font-family: Book Antiqua,Palatino; font-size: medium;">These are non-biased reviews &#8211; anyone can leave one! This is one thing that sets us apart from other sharpening companies.</span></li>
</ol>
<p><span style="font-family: Book Antiqua,Palatino; font-size: medium;">But as always, we would also love to hear your input here, so please feel free to leave a comment!</span></p>
			</div><!-- .entry-content -->
